273
00:17:51,060 --> 00:17:51,940
He should have

274
00:17:52,540 --> 00:17:54,180
been honest with me

275
00:17:54,900 --> 00:17:56,660
from the very start.

276
00:17:57,940 --> 00:17:58,780
