00:18:23,700 --> 00:18:25,300
I just

286
00:18:27,780 --> 00:18:29,210
can't get past this.

287
00:18:33,220 --> 00:18:34,060
But

288
00:18:38,700 --> 00:18:40,020
I can't sleep at all.

289
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:42,300
Right now,

290
00:18:43,220 --> 00:18:44,820
he's all I can think about.

291
00:18:45,780 --> 00:18:47,380
When I open my eyes, it's him.

292
00:18:47,900 --> 00:18:49,660
When I close them, it's still him.

293
00:18:50,420 --> 00:18:52,340
No matter what I do,

294
00:18:52,340 --> 00:18:54,580
he's always right there, in front of me.

295
00:18:54,580 --> 00:18:56,140
I just can't stop thinking about him.

296
00:18:56,140 --> 00:18:57,100
What do I do,

297
00:18:57,100 --> 00:18:57,940
Xinran?

298
00:18:59,140 --> 00:19:00,070
Okay, Yuan,

299
00:19:00,080 --> 00:19:01,690
let's not think about anything for now.

300
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:03,220
Just clear your mind, alright?

301
00:19:08,340 --> 00:19:09,820
I've already prepared your breakfast.

302
00:19:09,820 --> 00:19:10,940
Eat some in a little while.

303
00:19:13,460 --> 00:19:14,460
I won't bother you anymore.

304
00:19:14,460 --> 00:19:16,500
Take some time
to calm down and think, okay?

305
00:19:47,460 --> 00:19:48,300
How did it go?

306
00:19:48,300 --> 00:19:49,580
- Did Yao answer?
- Sorry.

307
00:19:50,050 --> 00:19:51,730
The number you dialed is currently busy.

308
00:19:52,620 --> 00:19:54,580
She's not answering
to calls or messages.

309
00:19:56,060 --> 00:19:57,080
That's strange.

310
00:19:57,500 --> 00:19:59,020
Yao is never late.

311
00:19:59,170 --> 00:20:00,510
Could something have happened?

312
00:20:01,620 --> 00:20:02,500
Stop overthinking.

313
00:20:02,500 --> 00:20:04,100
Maybe she'd come with Master.

314
00:20:05,660 --> 00:20:06,500
Anlan.

315
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:08,380
Hey, Master.

316
00:20:15,340 --> 00:20:16,540
Hey, Master.

317
00:20:22,350 --> 00:20:24,100
Master looks really upset.

318
00:20:24,370 --> 00:20:25,580
Did they have a fight?

319
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:30,020
They must have fallen out

320
00:20:30,020 --> 00:20:32,260
over Ancheng's acquisition
of Yao's uncle's restaurant.

321
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,900
Yao hasn't even shown up for her shift.

322
00:20:36,470 --> 00:20:37,740
It must be serious.

323
00:20:38,220 --> 00:20:39,060
Yeah.

324
00:20:41,580 --> 00:20:42,660
The inspection report is out.

325
00:20:43,420 --> 00:20:44,260
Leave me, please.

326
00:20:50,460 --> 00:20:52,540
(Sample Material Inspection Report)

327
00:20:52,540 --> 00:20:56,380
(Inspection Result: Failed)

328
00:21:13,260 --> 00:21:14,340
When did you find out?

329
00:21:16,140 --> 00:21:17,500
I didn't have any impression
of Yao Yuan.

330
00:21:18,380 --> 00:21:20,500
Chen and Uncle remembered her
and told me.

331
00:21:21,430 --> 00:21:22,660
When Yao Yuan came looking for you,

332
00:21:22,660 --> 00:21:23,650
why didn't you tell me?

333
00:21:24,750 --> 00:21:26,920
If I did, would it have helped?

334
00:21:28,940 --> 00:21:30,810
At least I wouldn't
have been caught off guard

335
00:21:30,810 --> 00:21:32,680
and be helpless to respond
to Yao Yuan's questions.

336
00:21:34,540 --> 00:21:35,380
Why?

337
00:21:36,120 --> 00:21:37,390
It wasn't in the plan,

338
00:21:37,740 --> 00:21:38,880
so it surprised you?

339
00:21:41,820 --> 00:21:42,660
Ancheng,

340
00:21:43,620 --> 00:21:44,460
why?

341
00:21:45,660 --> 00:21:47,780
Are you, like Aunt,
against us being together?

342
00:21:49,540 --> 00:21:51,500
Who you're with isn't my concern.

343
00:21:52,980 --> 00:21:53,820
I know.

344
00:21:54,620 --> 00:21:56,340
You've always treated that as a stain,

345
00:21:57,100 --> 00:21:58,100
and for a long time,

346
00:21:58,100 --> 00:21:58,940
you refused to forgive us.

347
00:22:00,100 --> 00:22:00,940
But don't forget,

348
00:22:01,660 --> 00:22:02,940
you're part of the Jiang family.

349
00:22:04,260 --> 00:22:05,580
If that was a mistake,

350
00:22:06,660 --> 00:22:08,020
you're part of that mistake as well.

351
00:22:09,660 --> 00:22:11,220
So you told Yao Yuan all this

352
00:22:11,220 --> 00:22:12,740
before we got married.

353
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:13,620
Was that your way

354
00:22:13,620 --> 00:22:15,020
of warning me about my mistake?

355
00:22:15,030 --> 00:22:16,040
Don't put this all on me.

356
00:22:16,940 --> 00:22:17,980
You should've told Yao Yuan

357
00:22:17,980 --> 00:22:18,940
yourself from the start.

358
00:22:20,460 --> 00:22:21,900
Were you planning to hide it
until after the wedding,

359
00:22:22,300 --> 00:22:23,260
so she'd find out herself?

360
00:22:24,580 --> 00:22:26,020
I have my own approach.

361
00:22:27,260 --> 00:22:28,300
She has the right to know.

362
00:22:31,260 --> 00:22:32,100
Anlan,

363
00:22:32,780 --> 00:22:33,620
I really want to ask you.

364
00:22:34,740 --> 00:22:36,180
Knowing who Yao Yuan is,

365
00:22:36,180 --> 00:22:37,020
why did you still pursue her?

366
00:22:38,180 --> 00:22:39,420
Was it just out of pity,

367
00:22:40,460 --> 00:22:41,300
to make up for her?

368
00:22:43,340 --> 00:22:45,580
I fell in love with her a long time ago,

369
00:22:46,020 --> 00:22:47,260
but I never imagined my family

370
00:22:47,260 --> 00:22:48,810
would cause such destruction to her.

371
00:22:52,300 --> 00:22:53,140
I thought

372
00:22:53,700 --> 00:22:55,300
you were confused by your own sympathy.

373
00:22:56,420 --> 00:22:57,260
What do you mean?

374
00:23:00,220 --> 00:23:01,260
Maybe you don't realize it,

375
00:23:02,380 --> 00:23:03,740
but you've always
been better than others.

376
00:23:04,980 --> 00:23:06,340
At some point,

377
00:23:07,580 --> 00:23:08,460
you started seeing

378
00:23:09,700 --> 00:23:11,500
helping others as a way
to show off your compassion.

379
00:23:12,740 --> 00:23:14,580
You keep telling our parents
how much you admire me.

380
00:23:15,940 --> 00:23:17,300
When you left Jiulong Group,

381
00:23:17,300 --> 00:23:18,620
you thought you were helping me.

382
00:23:19,620 --> 00:23:20,460
Anlan,

383
00:23:21,780 --> 00:23:22,620
feeling sorry for someone

384
00:23:23,660 --> 00:23:25,860
means you already think
you're better than them.

385
00:23:28,420 --> 00:23:29,260
Honestly,

386
00:23:30,300 --> 00:23:31,860
I really don't like you pitying me.

387
00:23:35,020 --> 00:23:36,460
So that's how you see it.

388
00:23:37,860 --> 00:23:38,700
Alright, now I get it.

389
00:23:39,900 --> 00:23:41,580
You just want to see me suffer.

390
00:23:43,100 --> 00:23:43,940
Ancheng.

391
00:23:44,900 --> 00:23:46,100
I don't want to say it again.

392
00:23:47,020 --> 00:23:47,860
You're my brother.

393
00:23:48,900 --> 00:23:50,750
I've never once felt sorry for you.

394
00:23:51,360 --> 00:23:52,950
I respect you. I even like you.

395
00:23:53,660 --> 00:23:55,220
I left Jiulong purely because

396
00:23:55,220 --> 00:23:56,580
I didn't want to witness what happened

397
00:23:56,580 --> 00:23:57,610
to Yao Yuan's parents again.

398
00:23:59,420 --> 00:24:00,560
I thought my silent protest

399
00:24:00,560 --> 00:24:01,610
could change something.

400
00:24:03,100 --> 00:24:04,260
But your actions

401
00:24:04,940 --> 00:24:06,060
have already made you someone

402
00:24:06,060 --> 00:24:07,300
people feel sorry for.

403
00:24:09,100 --> 00:24:11,340
With your ability,
you shouldn't be like this.

404
00:24:14,140 --> 00:24:14,980
I'm leaving, Ancheng.

405
00:25:02,210 --> 00:25:05,110
♪Waiting for dusk♪

406
00:25:06,250 --> 00:25:09,050
♪Waiting for the deep night♪

407
00:25:10,070 --> 00:25:16,730
♪Want to say goodnight
to you before sleep♪

408
00:25:18,280 --> 00:25:20,670
♪Never thought♪

409
00:25:21,020 --> 00:25:26,020
♪If you'd still be by my side
the next night♪

410
00:25:27,050 --> 00:25:31,810
♪No matter what,
we must cherish the present♪

411
00:25:34,260 --> 00:25:38,280
♪Arguing and bickering with you♪

412
00:25:38,280 --> 00:25:42,980
♪So that you can please me♪

413
00:25:43,210 --> 00:25:45,300
♪Stay with you till the end♪

414
00:25:45,300 --> 00:25:52,260
♪Whenever you need,
I'm always ready♪

415
00:25:59,340 --> 00:26:01,580
All the files are saved
on this USB drive.

416
00:26:01,900 --> 00:26:03,420
If you don't understand anything,

417
00:26:03,820 --> 00:26:04,780
feel free to ask me.

418
00:26:05,260 --> 00:26:06,100
Alright.

419
00:26:06,540 --> 00:26:08,100
But are you really going to quit?

420
00:26:08,820 --> 00:26:09,820
Why so sudden?

421
00:26:11,340 --> 00:26:12,180
Yeah, exactly.

422
00:26:13,220 --> 00:26:14,900
Oh, I get it now.

423
00:26:14,900 --> 00:26:16,170
You're preparing for the wedding.

424
00:26:18,540 --> 00:26:19,680
Anlan, you're here.

425
00:26:20,020 --> 00:26:21,900
Master, what's going on?
Yuan is quitting.

426
00:26:23,460 --> 00:26:24,300
Take care.

427
00:26:24,660 --> 00:26:25,500
You too.

428
00:26:26,020 --> 00:26:27,540
I will, thank you.

429
00:26:28,540 --> 00:26:29,380
Boss.

430
00:26:39,260 --> 00:26:40,100
Take a few days off.

431
00:26:40,860 --> 00:26:41,900
Come back when you're ready.

432
00:26:46,980 --> 00:26:47,820
No need.

433
00:26:49,060 --> 00:26:49,900
You know what it is.

434
00:26:50,860 --> 00:26:51,860
I've made up my mind.

435
00:27:00,340 --> 00:27:01,180
Hey, Yao.

436
00:27:02,060 --> 00:27:04,860
I heard breakups
peak right before weddings.

437
00:27:05,700 --> 00:27:07,740
Li Ao, what's really going on?

438
00:27:11,180 --> 00:27:12,020
Are you really leaving?

439
00:27:15,260 --> 00:27:16,980
Don't waste any more time on me.

440
00:27:18,900 --> 00:27:19,940
Focus your energy

441
00:27:20,660 --> 00:27:22,020
on things that really matter.

442
00:27:22,820 --> 00:27:24,140
You are what matters most.

443
00:27:26,180 --> 00:27:27,660
I know you're mad at me and my family.

444
00:27:28,860 --> 00:27:30,540
But the best way to get back at them

445
00:27:30,540 --> 00:27:31,740
is to be with me.

446
00:27:32,820 --> 00:27:34,060
Just be with me and treat me...

447
00:27:34,060 --> 00:27:35,220
I won't get back at them.

448
00:27:37,100 --> 00:27:38,140
I don't have that kind of power.

449
00:27:41,020 --> 00:27:43,700
And I would never drag you
into it or blame you.

450
00:27:45,420 --> 00:27:46,260
It's just that

451
00:27:48,540 --> 00:27:49,660
I really don't know

452
00:27:49,660 --> 00:27:51,100
how I'm supposed to be with you.

453
00:27:54,980 --> 00:27:56,500
I know you can't forgive me

454
00:27:56,500 --> 00:27:57,340
for hiding things from you.

455
00:27:58,260 --> 00:27:59,260
I did make mistakes.

456
00:28:01,060 --> 00:28:02,140
But my feelings for you

457
00:28:02,140 --> 00:28:03,380
were never anything but real.

458
00:28:04,820 --> 00:28:06,380
I don't want to think about this now.

459
00:28:12,300 --> 00:28:13,620
We shouldn't see each other anymore.

460
00:28:20,100 --> 00:28:21,260
Tell me you don't love me.

461
00:28:24,300 --> 00:28:25,340
I fought so hard

462
00:28:25,340 --> 00:28:26,540
just to be with you.

463
00:28:27,460 --> 00:28:28,340
No matter what happens,

464
00:28:28,340 --> 00:28:29,820
I won't let you go easily.

465
00:28:32,700 --> 00:28:33,540
I'll wait for you

466
00:28:35,500 --> 00:28:36,740
until the day you accept me.

467
00:28:48,020 --> 00:28:48,860
But I...

468
00:28:49,740 --> 00:28:50,980
Every time I see you now,

469
00:28:53,180 --> 00:28:54,660
I can't help but think of my parents.

470
00:28:57,100 --> 00:28:58,140
What am I supposed to do?

471
00:29:43,900 --> 00:29:44,740
Boss.

472
00:29:47,220 --> 00:29:48,060
Boss.

473
00:29:48,660 --> 00:29:49,500
Are you okay?

474
00:29:50,380 --> 00:29:51,820
Should I cancel the meeting?

475
00:29:53,740 --> 00:29:54,580
No need.

476
00:29:54,980 --> 00:29:55,860
Give me the files.

477
00:30:02,220 --> 00:30:04,180
(Company Employee Rewards
Yao Yuan, Fang Jianing)

478
00:30:06,980 --> 00:30:08,020
This month's expenses

479
00:30:08,020 --> 00:30:09,740
include some from the Xiduomeng Project.

480
00:30:10,660 --> 00:30:12,580
Also, next month's financial plan

481
00:30:12,580 --> 00:30:13,420
needs your review.

482
00:30:15,580 --> 00:30:16,420
Boss.

483
00:30:18,380 --> 00:30:19,220
Boss.

484
00:30:19,980 --> 00:30:20,820
Ah?

485
00:30:23,100 --> 00:30:23,940
Don't push yourself.

486
00:30:24,700 --> 00:30:25,980
I'll cancel the meeting for you.

487
00:30:27,900 --> 00:30:28,740
Okay.

488
00:31:15,220 --> 00:31:16,900
Ziyun Mountain got its name

489
00:31:18,620 --> 00:31:19,740
because it's purple.

490
00:31:21,060 --> 00:31:22,260
And Picasso believed that

491
00:31:23,340 --> 00:31:24,380
blue is special.

492
00:31:26,140 --> 00:31:27,580
In ancient Egypt's tradition,

493
00:31:28,740 --> 00:31:29,740
it symbolizes hell

494
00:31:31,740 --> 00:31:32,780
and stands for death.

495
00:31:34,180 --> 00:31:35,180
The appearance of blue

496
00:31:35,180 --> 00:31:36,860
means a path to death

497
00:31:37,420 --> 00:31:38,260
is unfolding.

498
00:31:40,100 --> 00:31:42,340
Ziyun Mountain is painted with blue,

499
00:31:44,300 --> 00:31:46,140
turning from a dating spot

500
00:31:46,140 --> 00:31:47,380
into a place for breakups.

501
00:31:50,300 --> 00:31:51,140
But

502
00:31:53,220 --> 00:31:54,460
since you painted Ziyun Mountain,

503
00:31:55,860 --> 00:31:57,020
it shows you still care.

504
00:31:59,420 --> 00:32:00,260
Yao Yuan,

505
00:32:01,060 --> 00:32:02,780
can you really bury this relationship?

506
00:32:10,060 --> 00:32:10,900
No matter what,

507
00:32:14,020 --> 00:32:14,980
what's meant to end

508
00:32:16,620 --> 00:32:17,900
will end sooner or later.

509
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:23,140
Now's not the time to force yourself.

510
00:32:24,620 --> 00:32:25,700
That only makes it hurt more.

511
00:32:27,860 --> 00:32:29,020
No matter what happens,

512
00:32:29,740 --> 00:32:31,060
we've always been here.

513
00:32:32,220 --> 00:32:33,300
There's no room for weakness.

514
00:32:34,420 --> 00:32:35,460
You were never truly alone.

515
00:32:54,620 --> 00:32:57,940
(Hurun Report)

516
00:32:58,700 --> 00:33:00,500
Dad, Mom made you ginseng tea.

517
00:33:01,100 --> 00:33:01,940
Just leave it there.

518
00:33:02,340 --> 00:33:03,180
Ancheng.

519
00:33:05,420 --> 00:33:06,300
How's Anlan doing lately?

520
00:33:07,540 --> 00:33:08,700
I haven't seen him for days.

521
00:33:09,060 --> 00:33:10,980
Weren't you two working
on the project together?

522
00:33:13,180 --> 00:33:15,380
Seems it's because of Miss Yao.

523
00:33:16,260 --> 00:33:17,500
Anlan doesn't seem focused.

524
00:33:20,020 --> 00:33:21,260
Did something happen between them?

525
00:33:22,540 --> 00:33:23,380
Looks like they broke up.

526
00:33:25,260 --> 00:33:26,940
Anlan must be feeling terrible.

527
00:33:28,750 --> 00:33:29,590
Right.

528
00:33:30,300 --> 00:33:32,020
Now, Li Ao is managing the company.

529
00:33:56,060 --> 00:33:57,620
Go to your grandma's
and clear your mind.

530
00:33:58,060 --> 00:33:59,060
I'll come find you later.

531
00:33:59,780 --> 00:34:01,500
Got it. Don't worry about me.

532
00:34:01,500 --> 00:34:02,620
I'll take good care of myself.

533
00:34:03,100 --> 00:34:04,740
Remember to call me when you arrive.

534
00:34:04,740 --> 00:34:06,260
Alright, I'm off. Bye.

535
00:34:06,460 --> 00:34:07,380
Okay, bye.

536
00:34:23,020 --> 00:34:23,940
Why are you here?

537
00:34:25,860 --> 00:34:27,860
Just trying my luck,

538
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:29,820
seeing if I have a chance

539
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:30,700
to be your knight.

540
00:34:31,460 --> 00:34:33,580
Didn't expect to wait only four days

541
00:34:33,580 --> 00:34:34,420
to see you.

542
00:34:34,940 --> 00:34:35,900
Am I really that lucky?

543
00:34:38,740 --> 00:34:39,580
Thank you.

544
00:34:40,420 --> 00:34:42,610
But lately, I might not...

545
00:34:43,300 --> 00:34:44,760
You believe whatever others say?

546
00:34:45,140 --> 00:34:46,500
I didn't wait just four days.

547
00:34:46,860 --> 00:34:49,020
Xinran told Wen Cheng
you'd go find your grandma,

548
00:34:49,500 --> 00:34:51,380
so he asked me to come over

549
00:34:51,380 --> 00:34:52,340
to look after you for Anlan.

550
00:34:57,100 --> 00:34:58,820
If you still consider me a friend,

551
00:34:58,820 --> 00:34:59,660
don't shut me out.

552
00:35:00,220 --> 00:35:01,060
Alright?

553
00:35:03,820 --> 00:35:04,660
Let's go.

554
00:35:05,820 --> 00:35:07,660
Just treat me like I'm invisible
on this trip.

555
00:35:08,220 --> 00:35:09,710
Pretend I'm not here.

556
00:35:10,160 --> 00:35:11,000
Let's get going.

557
00:35:20,770 --> 00:35:22,100
How's Yuan doing today?

558
00:35:22,900 --> 00:35:25,020
Shouldn't you be calling to check on me?

559
00:35:26,100 --> 00:35:27,460
Who are you inquiring for?

560
00:35:28,440 --> 00:35:29,280
Jiang Anlan.

561
00:35:30,780 --> 00:35:33,320
Don't worry, she's already at Grandma's.

562
00:35:34,500 --> 00:35:35,380
I'm wondering

563
00:35:35,380 --> 00:35:37,300
when will those two finally make up.

564
00:35:37,300 --> 00:35:39,060
How long do we have to
keep passing messages?

565
00:35:40,140 --> 00:35:41,820
Even if it takes ten years,
we have to help.

566
00:35:42,050 --> 00:35:42,900
Don't forget,

567
00:35:42,910 --> 00:35:43,940
